Package com.orchestranetworks.service Description

Provides classes and interfaces for implementing specific services and access rules on EBX5.

Services

In EBX5, there are two type of services:

  • A UI service is integrated into Manager sessions – see ServiceContext.
  • A programmatic service is called externally, for example from a batch or from a web service implementation – see ProgrammaticService.

If a service has to perform any update on data in EBX5, it has to implement a Procedure.

Access Rules

In EBX5, access to data may be restricted programmatically – see AccessRule.
